{"tid":683393,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"(又係遵理) Guy Leung 2018 全新神抄之塔，又又又抄！","createTime":"2018-05-29T15:59:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-30T13:06:29.000Z","uid":97608,"like":38,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"5afebde2f384b99bc6685549630142c4f319123f","tid":683393,"uid":97608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T15:59:46.000Z","msg":"近排燈塔真係好熱鬧，又上市失敗又老師互鬥<br />\n好戲當然要繼續先過癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今次爆大獲既對象仍然係抄襲之王 Guy Leung。<br />\n自從舊年抄襲同校康蛇搞到潛水半年之後，再次出水。<br />\n勢估唔到仲死性不改，繼續抄抄抄！<br />\n<br />\n今日醒左少少唔係100%照Copy，但明顯題目、論據完全一樣<br />\n甚至次序都唔調下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n歡迎巴打提供更多線索同埋內幕，來緊幾日繼續爆更大獲野！<br />\n保證好睇過TBB<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次又賴助教？<br />\n最新章程仲講到明全部100%自己做，點解釋<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/29/235611_94dc29d79e9d8db41dcf9cde968e4371.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F29%2F235611_94dc29d79e9d8db41dcf9cde968e4371.png&h=4f1d8df3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一題抄襲：齡記出版社<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/29/235620_e76a2880cb05357b410f57fe990de4e1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F29%2F235620_e76a2880cb05357b410f57fe990de4e1.png&h=8a49d178&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nGuy Leung 筆記，一Q樣<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/29/235628_62bf1edb36141f114521ec4bb4175579.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F29%2F235628_62bf1edb36141f114521ec4bb4175579.jpg&h=c9ad8798&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/29/235633_134ce63057f068a219a0df338fb0b723.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F29%2F235633_134ce63057f068a219a0df338fb0b723.jpg&h=acfc653b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/29/235638_daa79432b242c16e82493597a4d8c41f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F29%2F235638_daa79432b242c16e82493597a4d8c41f.jpg&h=ad99049a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/29/235641_9876c9a3f300f29c8ee619765c1ad768.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F29%2F235641_9876c9a3f300f29c8ee619765c1ad768.jpg&h=1ad49b1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第二題抄襲：繼續齡記<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/29/235656_07a64e19874e7dce4824b30730ef17fa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F29%2F235656_07a64e19874e7dce4824b30730ef17fa.png&h=b79ada8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nGuy Leung 筆記，一Q樣<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/29/235704_840b332d939dc4280b44adfff9bb2f0a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F29%2F235704_840b332d939dc4280b44adfff9bb2f0a.jpg&h=b4569767&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/29/235709_fb4118cdd8021b024746147b02b5fda4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F29%2F235709_fb4118cdd8021b024746147b02b5fda4.jpg&h=fefe3552&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/29/235713_5f07945a6aa5fd2c6574d03d99f4e35a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F29%2F235713_5f07945a6aa5fd2c6